∀ {E : Type u_1} {F : Type u_2} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] [inst_2 : CompleteSpace E]
  [inst_3 : TopologicalSpace F] [inst_4 : ChartedSpace E F] [inst_5 : SmoothManifoldWithCorners (ModelWithCornersSelf ℂ E) F]
  {f : F → E} {γ : Path E}, (∀ z, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → γ.isClosed → ∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z = 0

∀ {E : Type u} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : ℂ → ℂ} {z₀ : ℂ},
  HolomorphicOn f (Metric.ball z₀ 1) →
    ContinuousOn γ (Set.Icc 0 1) →
    (γ 0 = γ 1) →
      (∮ z in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : ℂ → ℂ} {s : Set ℂ},
  ContinuousOn γ s →
    (∀ z ∈ s, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) →
      (∀ t : ℝ, γ t = γ 0 → γ t = γ 1) → (∮ (z : ℂ) in Path γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] [inst_2 : CompleteSpace E] 
  {f : ℂ → E} {γ : ℂ → ℂ} (holo : ∀ z, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z),
  (∮ z in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] [inst_2 : CompleteSpace E]
  {f : ℂ → E} {γ : ℂ → ℂ}, IsHolomorphicOn γ (Set.range γ) f → ∮ (z : ℂ) in Curve γ, f z = 0

∀ {E : Type u} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : ℂ → ℂ},
  (∀ z, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → Path.IsClosed γ → (∮ z, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : ℂ → ℂ)
  (hγ : IsClosedPath γ), (∀ z, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → (∮ z in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : ℂ → ℂ},
  IsHolomorphic f → IsClosedLoop γ → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0
